lyrics:
(Chorus)
Floating, falling, through the ether calling,
In the echo of the void, where the stars are stalling.
Disconnected hearts, in a world apart,
Searching for a start, in the art of the dark.

(Outro)
In the glow of screens, we find our scenes,
Crafting dreams within digital streams.
Though the night is long, we'll sing our songs,
In the art of the dark, where we belong.
